/* ==========================================================
   KidCoder – Adventure Module (v3 – UNIQUE MINI-GAMES)
   Each stop has its own interactive game that tests coding
   skills the kid learned: code tracing, debugging, sorting
   code blocks, true/false knowledge, variable tracking.
   NO redirects to quiz/logic — everything plays inline.
   ========================================================== */

/* ---------- Game type legend ----------
   code_output  → Show code, pick what it prints
   bug_hunt     → Find the buggy line in code
   true_false   → Quick Prawda/Fałsz statements
   sort_code    → Click code blocks in correct order
   var_tracker  → Trace variable value through code
   ---------------------------------------- */

