        options: ["5", "6", "8", "13"],
        correct: 2,
        explanation: "To ciąg Fibonacciego! f(0)=0, f(1)=1, f(2)=1, f(3)=2, f(4)=3, f(5)=5, f(6)=8 🎉"
      },
    ],
  },
